    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Euconnus motschulskii. 1, male, dorsal habitus (scale: 1 mm); 2, labrum (scale: 0.2 mm); 3, right madible (scale: 0.2 mm); 4, maxilla (scale: 0.2 mm); 5, antennae of male (scale: 0.2 mm); 6, aedeagus, dorsal aspect (scale: 0.2 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219467/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219469>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 22. 15, Euconnus goerzensis, antennae of male (scale: 0.2 mm); 16, E. goerzensis, aedeagus, dorsal aspect (scale: 0.1 mm); 17, E. ispartaensis, antennae of male (scale: 0.2 mm); 18, E. ispartaensis, aedeagus, dorsal aspect (scale: 0.1 mm); 19, E. meybohmi, antennae of male (scale: 0.2 mm); 20, E. meybohmi, aedeagus, dorsal aspect (scale: 0.1 mm); 21, E. robustus, antennae of male (scale: 0.2 mm); 22, E. robustus, aedeagus, dorsal aspect (scale: 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219469/files/figure.png" ;
